*** 7. DUT INSTANTIATION ***
* Crucial: Order matches your PEX extracted netlist precisely!
X1 VSS VDD le clk rst_n rst_override_n din[0] clk_n din[11] din[10] 
+ din[9] din[8] din[7] din[6] din[5] din[4] din[3] din[2] din[1] din[12] din[13] din[15]
+ din[14] address[0] address[1] address[11] address[7] address[8] address[6] address[4]
+ address[3] address[13] address[14] address[12] address[9] address[2] address[15]
+ address[10] address[5] dout[1] dout[2] dout[3] dout[4] dout[5] dout[6] dout[7] dout[15]
+ dout[14] dout[13] dout[12] dout[11] dout[10] dout[9] dout[8] dout[0] oeb bus_enable 
+ web unused[0] unused[1] unused[2] unused[3] unused[4] unused[5] unused[6] 
+ fl_mcpu32

*** 8. ANALYSIS & PRINT CONTROL ***
*.DC V_VDD 0 3.3 0.33
.DC V_VDD 3.3 3.3 0.33

.PRINT DC V(VDD) V(le) V(oeb) V(web) V(bus_enable)
.PRINT DC V(address[0]) V(address[1]) V(address[2]) V(address[3]) V(address[4]) V(address[5]) V(address[6]) V(address[7])
.PRINT DC V(address[8]) V(address[9]) V(address[10]) V(address[11]) V(address[12]) V(address[13]) V(address[14]) V(address[15])
.PRINT DC V(dout[0]) V(dout[1]) V(dout[2]) V(dout[3]) V(dout[4]) V(dout[5]) V(dout[6]) V(dout[7])
.PRINT DC V(dout[8]) V(dout[9]) V(dout[10]) V(dout[11]) V(dout[12]) V(dout[13]) V(dout[14]) V(dout[15])

* --- Current Measurements for all Voltage Sources ---

* Power and Control Signals
.PRINT DC I(V_VSS) I(V_VDD) I(V_clk) I(V_clk_n) I(V_rst_n) I(V_rst_override_n)

* Lower Byte Data Inputs
.PRINT DC I(V_din0) I(V_din1) I(V_din2) I(V_din3) I(V_din4) I(V_din5) I(V_din6) I(V_din7)

* Upper Byte Data Inputs
